nodes.text: A gartro egg omelet was a dish made from gartro eggs and jerba cheese. They were served at Dex's Diner for 7.5 credits where fillings of either diced gornt, diced roba, Felucian glasscap mushrooms, Ferroan spinach, Bellassan peppers, Ojomian onions, topatoes or calarantrum root were available for an extra 0.5 credits.
